# App-to-Port Registry — sample/scaffold
# Promote to app-port-registry.csv after review, then wire into Vector (Phase 2).
#
# Fields:
#   port        - integer destination port (or source port if direction=src)
#   protocol    - TCP, UDP, or * (both)
#   app         - short label written to the 'app' field in flow documents
#   category    - infrastructure, storage, database, monitoring, network, k8s, security
#   direction   - dst (match dst_port), src (match src_port), both
#   scope       - internal (RFC1918 only), external, or blank (any)
#   notes       - free text, not used by Vector
port,protocol,app,category,direction,scope,notes
# --- Common well-known ports (already in Vector VRL hardcoded map) ---
22,TCP,SSH,infrastructure,dst,,Secure Shell
25,TCP,SMTP,infrastructure,dst,,SMTP relay
53,UDP,DNS,network,dst,,DNS queries
53,TCP,DNS,network,dst,,DNS over TCP (zone transfers / large responses)
80,TCP,HTTP,web,dst,,HTTP
110,TCP,POP3,infrastructure,dst,,POP3
123,UDP,NTP,infrastructure,dst,,NTP time sync
143,TCP,IMAP,infrastructure,dst,,IMAP
161,UDP,SNMP,monitoring,dst,,SNMP polling
162,UDP,SNMP,monitoring,dst,,SNMP traps
443,TCP,HTTPS,web,dst,,HTTPS
445,TCP,SMB,storage,dst,,SMB/CIFS file sharing
465,TCP,SMTP,infrastructure,dst,,SMTP over TLS
587,TCP,SMTP,infrastructure,dst,,SMTP submission
853,TCP,DNS-TLS,network,dst,,DNS-over-TLS
993,TCP,IMAP,infrastructure,dst,,IMAP over TLS
995,TCP,POP3,infrastructure,dst,,POP3 over TLS
1194,UDP,OpenVPN,security,dst,,OpenVPN
1883,TCP,MQTT,iot,dst,,MQTT
2049,TCP,NFS,storage,dst,,NFS data plane
2049,UDP,NFS,storage,dst,,NFS data plane (UDP)
3000,TCP,Grafana,monitoring,dst,,Grafana dashboard
3306,TCP,MySQL,database,dst,,MySQL
5432,TCP,Postgres,database,dst,,PostgreSQL
6379,TCP,Redis,database,dst,,Redis
6443,TCP,Kubernetes,k8s,dst,,Kubernetes API server
8006,TCP,Proxmox,infrastructure,dst,,Proxmox VE web UI and API
8080,TCP,HTTP-Alt,web,dst,,HTTP alternate port
8443,TCP,HTTPS-Alt,web,dst,,HTTPS alternate port
9000,TCP,MinIO,storage,dst,,MinIO S3-compatible object storage
9090,TCP,Prometheus,monitoring,dst,,Prometheus metrics API
9093,TCP,Alertmanager,monitoring,dst,,Prometheus Alertmanager
9100,TCP,NodeExporter,monitoring,dst,,Prometheus node_exporter
9200,TCP,OpenSearch,storage,dst,,OpenSearch REST API
9300,TCP,OpenSearch-Transport,storage,dst,,OpenSearch inter-node transport
51820,UDP,WireGuard,security,dst,,WireGuard VPN
